documents:
The obs table keeps a record of all the data coming from an OpenMRS HTML form.
Every record in obs has a concept_id column, which holds the meaning of the concept in the related table concepts

Drugs have their names saved in OpenMRS concept_name table called Dictionary. Most records in the obs table has a concept_id which can be located at the concept_name table. Note: concept_name is related to concept table through concept_id
